messages.messageBody:
Hi everyone,

Shyrley wanted me to post an update for her.

I finally talked with her on IM today. She had her natural delivery
on the 9th, but things didn't go well. Baby wasn't breathing
after the delivery and Shyrley lost lots of blood. :(

They were both rushed to the hospital. Shyrley ended up with some
infections, but got to come home this afternoon. Baby, Celyn,
isn't doing as well. She has brain damage. :( She is breathing
on her on now, but they think she possibly has Cerebral Palsy.

So, keep Shyrley and her baby in your thoughts. If anyone wants
more info, you can e-mail me off list.

Kelli~
